name: Expanse
description: The artwork «Expanse» is a metaphorical view of the ecological catastrophe, a call to conscious consumption of resources. The remnants of human civilization of the city of Pripyat are gradually dissolving, nature is gaining space back, houses are sprouted with trees, creating landscapes of the post-humanity world. Nature quietly dissolves the whole environment, humanity has not been able to coexist in harmony with the world. 8192x4920 px, JPG, 5,91 MB
